# meta-secret-compose — Cursor Entry Point

This is the **Compose/iOS/Android UI layer** of MetaSecret. The AI brain is in `.ai/`.

## First Read (before any code change)

1. **`.ai/ARCHITECTURE.md`** — Project structure & KMM patterns
2. **`.ai/agents/feature-planner.md`** — How to plan features
3. **`.ai/agents/code-implementer.md`** — Implementation patterns
4. **`.ai/skills/kmp-doctor/`** — KMM troubleshooting

## Key Rules

- **MVVM + Coordinator** — State in ViewModel, UI doesn't orchestrate
- **Shared module** — Business logic in KMM shared, UI platform-specific
- **Design tokens** — Never hardcode colors/spacing; use theme system
- **Compose** — Immutable state, proper recomposition scopes
- **SwiftUI** — @StateObject, @State for local state, proper binding patterns
- **Testing** — Unit tests for ViewModels, integration tests for UI coordination

