## Cursor Workflow

1. Open **Terminal** (Ctrl+`) in Cursor
2. Run a command: `/compose-only-planner "your feature"`
3. Cursor shows guidance and artifact links
4. Review in editor, continue iterating

## Important Context

- **This is meta-secret-compose** — KMM UI layer only
- **Meta-secret-core** is separate (crypto/protocol)
- **MetaSecret root** coordinates both repos
- To switch repos: go to MetaSecret root, use `/route` or `/core-only-*`

